graph TD
    subgraph Device ["User's Device  (Browser + OPFS)"]
        SQLite["SQLite Database\n(JSON-LD nodes + metadata)\n(primary data store)"]
        LoroCRDT["Loro CRDT State\n(binary deltas in SQLite)\n(ADR-045 — replaces Yjs)"]
        Commits["Sovereign Graph Commits\n(Loro snapshots + version log)\n(content-addressed)"]

        SQLite ---|"one node = one row\nchecksum per row"| SQLite
        LoroCRDT ---|"binary delta per mutation\nstate vector for sync"| LoroCRDT
        Commits ---|"immutable · parent chaining\nreplay → reconstruct state"| Commits

        SQLite -->|"CRDT state co-located"| LoroCRDT
        LoroCRDT -->|"snapshot = commit"| Commits
    end
